    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but calling my doctor every time i have a thought about my dose is a bit much. i've been doing my research and people say that if your levels are stable you can often taper down. since i feel so good right now, wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg be a safer way to transition instead of just staying on the high dose forever? it just feels like more of a logical approach for someone who's stable.",
