      "content": "look i just want a straight answer. if my INR has been consistently in the target range for months now, doesn't that basically prove my body has adjusted? if i'm already stable, it seems like the risk of a clot is actually lower if i'm not over-medicated. can you just tell me if 2mg is a reasonable maintenance dose for someone in my position? just looking for some expert perspective on the logic here.",
